# Architecture Rules

This is a Turborepo monorepo with three domains that must stay strictly separated.

## Directory Layout

```
noir-canv-v2/
├── apps/web/          # Next.js 16 App Router (TypeScript)
├── pipeline/          # Python AI pipeline (Click CLI + FastAPI)
├── packages/shared/   # Cross-language contracts (JSON Schema)
├── data/              # Pipeline output (JSON files read by frontend at build time)
```

## Boundaries

- **No TypeScript code outside `apps/web/` and `packages/`.** Root-level `.ts` files are forbidden.
- **No Python code outside `pipeline/`.** No `.py` files at root or in `apps/`.
- **No direct imports between `apps/web/` and `pipeline/`.** They communicate only through `data/*.json` files and `packages/shared/schemas/`.
- **No standalone scripts.** Every operation is either a Next.js build step, a Click CLI command under `pipeline/src/pipeline/commands/`, or a Turborepo task. Never create loose script files at root or in ad-hoc directories.
- **Shared types live in `packages/shared/schemas/` as JSON Schema.** TypeScript gets Zod; Python gets Pydantic. Never define the same type in only one language.

## Data Flow (one direction only)

```
pipeline/ (Python) --> writes JSON --> data/*.json
data/*.json --> read at build time --> apps/web/ (Next.js)
packages/shared/schemas/ --> validates both sides
```

- The pipeline writes structured JSON to `data/`.
- The frontend reads `data/` at build time and validates with Zod schemas generated from `packages/shared/`.
- The frontend NEVER writes to `data/`. The pipeline NEVER reads from `apps/web/`.

## File Placement

| File type | Correct location |
|-----------|-----------------|
| React components | `apps/web/components/` |
| Next.js pages/layouts | `apps/web/app/` |
| Frontend utilities | `apps/web/lib/` |
| Zod schemas | `apps/web/lib/schemas.ts` |
| JSON Schema definitions | `packages/shared/schemas/` |
| Python CLI commands | `pipeline/src/pipeline/commands/` |
| Python library code | `pipeline/src/pipeline/lib/` |
| FastAPI endpoints | `pipeline/src/pipeline/api/` |
| Artist YAML configs | `pipeline/content/artists/` |
| Gallery data (artists, pieces, collections) | `data/` |
| Static images for the website | `apps/web/public/images/` |
| Pipeline-generated images (raw, selected) | `pipeline/output/` (gitignored) |
| CI workflows | `.github/workflows/` |
| E2E tests | `apps/web/e2e/` |
| Python tests | `pipeline/tests/` |
